sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant GH as GitHub/GitLab
    participant Jira as Jira/Linear
    participant Chat as Slack/Teams
    participant Mail as Outlook/Gmail
    participant Conn as Connector Framework
    participant Capture as Context Capture Layer
    participant Store as State + Timeline Store
    participant Memory as Memory Subsystem
    participant Triage as Triage
    participant Core as LLM Reasoning Core
    participant Policy as Interaction / Attention Policy
    participant UI as Extension UI

    GH->>Conn: Review request
    Jira->>Conn: Assigned ticket
    Chat->>Conn: Mention
    Mail->>Conn: Important mail
    Conn->>Capture: Source signals
    Capture->>Capture: Normalize and dedup
    Capture->>Store: Append events
    Triage->>Store: Read open obligations
    Triage->>Memory: Read project context
    Triage->>Core: Rank urgency and importance
    Core-->>Triage: Ranked cited list
    Triage->>Policy: Candidate list
    Policy->>Policy: Check quiet rules
    Policy-->>UI: Propose what needs me now
